{
  "stem": "11174.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Japan-- well, the way we lived is-- was a chapter by itself.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't have enough for livelihoods.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was all money that came from America-- I think from the American Joint Distribution-- to a committee in Japan.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they gave us-- it was no kitchen-- to-- to-- they gave us some money.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was enough for-- and also a pound of rice bread again.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And very little money.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we got a few-- we got a place where to sleep.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was on the-- mattresses on the floors, Japanese style.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we-- a few-- three or four guys always got together to cook together-- those little hibachi ovens.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] And some how got a pot and we used to go out on the market and buy bananas that were put on the side, so had already black spots, and onions and noodles.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Noodles were very cheap there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we made all-- potatoes with noodles, made a soup.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And with a little oil-- oil was also very cheap.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we have a meal every day like this, and this kept us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And at night, we had some of these bananas that was, the fruit and vegetables.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And somehow there's nothing that I can think of that is out of the ordinary too much-- Do you remember--",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--to talk about.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Those-- that-- that time-- In Japan, what I planned I was hoping still to get-- I was-- I-- the-- the men that I wrote-- wrote to America about helping me getting some dollars.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I got from him a notification that he sent me $100, and it's in-- in-- in some bureau in Tokyo.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I-- going to Tokyo was too much money, and I didn't have it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I asked, but I didn't get to.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
